    dc:description "FIGURES 58–63. Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (58) dorsal view of male imago; (59) closer view of head and thorax of male imago; (60) abdominal terga of male imago; (61) head, dorsal view of male imago; (62) prosternal triangle of male imago; (62) prosternal triangle of female imago." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7773308>
    dc:description "FIGURES 64–67. Male imago of Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (64) foretarsi; (65) closer view of foretarsomere segment III; (66) male genitalia; (67) forceps and penis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773308/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7773315>
    dc:description "FIGURES 76–80. Larval exuvia of Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (76) maxilla; (77) labium; (78) paraglossa and labial palp; (79) mesonotum; (80) foreclaw." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7773317>
    dc:description "FIGURES 81–84. Larval exuvia of Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (81) foreleg; (82) forefemur; (83) transverse row of setation in forefemur; (84) midleg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773317/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7773319>
    dc:description "FIGURES 85–91. Larval exuvia of Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (85) midclaw; (86) hindfemur; (87) hindtibia and tarus; (88) hindtibia setation; (89) hindtarsus setation; (90) hindclaw; (91) closer view of hindclaw (arrow indicates three minute basal denticles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773319/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7773321>
    dc:description "FIGURES 92–96. Larval exuvia of Caenis venkataramani sp. n.: (92) dorsal view of tergalius II; (93) detail of microtrichia in tergalius II; (94) tergalius III; (95) hind margin of terga VII–X; (96) shape of sternum IX." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7773321/files/figure.png" ;
